long.ar,el,en,en_AU,en_GB,en_US,fa,fil,hi,hu,:
â¤ï¸Learn better with ChatGPT 
ğŸ’«How to use it?
â¡ï¸ After install this extension, it will jump to option Page. You can select and set API Provider
â¡ï¸ If you tend to use ChatGPT Webapp as AI Provider, It is free but sometimes unstable,and  mention you "Please login and pass Cloudflare".
â¡ï¸ So we recommend you use your own OpenAI API key. How to get your own OpenAI API key?
â¡ï¸ Login https://platform.openai.com and then click your personal account setting, you can see "View API keys".Finally Create a new secret key or copy the key that you created before.
â¡ï¸ Paste your OpenAI API key to AI Provider and save your config.You can get the summary alongside Google search results or Youtube videos summary now. 

ğŸ™‹Q&A
ğŸ‘‰Q1:What is ChatGPT?
ğŸš€A1:ChatGPT is an OpenAI-developed language model that utilizes a large pre-trained Transformer-based neural network to generate human-like text in response to user prompts. With its diverse range of training on internet text, ChatGPT can provide responses on various topics, such as general knowledge, conversations, and creative writing.

ğŸ‘‰Q2:What is Google/YouTube Summary with ChatGPT?
ğŸš€A2:It is an extension that displays a summary of ChatGPT in Google search results simultaneously.In addition,you can also get summary of the YouTube videos.

ğŸ‘‰Q3:Is Google/YouTube Summary with ChatGPT free?
ğŸš€Q3:Although our extension is currently free, we are exploring the possibility of introducing a small paywall to sustain the service in the future. By upgrading to the paid service, you will enjoy faster response times, unrestricted access, and high-priority customer support. Our ultimate goal is to provide you with the best possible service in a way that is affordable and accessible to everyone.

ğŸ‘‰Q4:Do I need to create a ChatGPT/OpenAI account to use this extension?
ğŸš€Q4:Yes, you must have a ChatGPT account to use this extension. You can create a free account at chat.openai.com.

ğŸ’«How to use it?
â¡ï¸ After install this extension, it will jump to option Page. You can select and set API Provider
â¡ï¸ If you tend to use ChatGPT Webapp as AI Provider, It is free but sometimes unstable,and  mention you "Please login and pass Cloudflare".
â¡ï¸ So we recommend you use your own OpenAI API key. How to get your own OpenAI API key?
â¡ï¸ Login https://platform.openai.com and then click your personal account setting, you can see "View API keys".Finally Create a new secret key or copy the key that you created before.
â¡ï¸ Paste your OpenAI API key to AI Provider and save your config.You can get the summary alongside Google search results or Youtube videos summary now. 

ğŸ™‹Q&A
ğŸ‘‰Q1:What is ChatGPT?
ğŸš€A1:ChatGPT is an OpenAI-developed language model that utilizes a large pre-trained Transformer-based neural network to generate human-like text in response to user prompts. With its diverse range of training on internet text, ChatGPT can provide responses on various topics, such as general knowledge, conversations, and creative writing.

ğŸ‘‰Q2:What is Google/YouTube Summary with ChatGPT?
ğŸš€A2:It is an extension that displays a summary of ChatGPT in Google search results simultaneously.In addition,you can also get summary of the YouTube videos.

ğŸ‘‰Q3:Is Google/YouTube Summary with ChatGPT free?
ğŸš€Q3:Although our extension is currently free, we are exploring the possibility of introducing a small paywall to sustain the service in the future. By upgrading to the paid service, you will enjoy faster response times, unrestricted access, and high-priority customer support. Our ultimate goal is to provide you with the best possible service in a way that is affordable and accessible to everyone.

ğŸ‘‰Q4:Do I need to create a ChatGPT/OpenAI account to use this extension?
ğŸš€Q4:Yes, you must have a ChatGPT account to use this extension. You can create a free account at chat.openai.com.

â¤ï¸Learn better with ChatGPT 
ğŸ’«How to use it?
â¡ï¸ After install this extension, it will jump to option Page. You can select and set API Provider
â¡ï¸ If you tend to use ChatGPT Webapp as AI Provider, It is free but sometimes unstable,and  mention you "Please login and pass Cloudflare".
â¡ï¸ So we recommend you use your own OpenAI API key. How to get your own OpenAI API key?
â¡ï¸ Login https://platform.openai.com and then click your personal account setting, you can see "View API keys".Finally Create a new secret key or copy the key that you created before.
â¡ï¸ Paste your OpenAI API key to AI Provider and save your config.You can get the summary alongside Google search results or Youtube videos summary now. 

ğŸ™‹Q&A
ğŸ‘‰Q1:What is ChatGPT?
ğŸš€A1:ChatGPT is an OpenAI-developed language model that utilizes a large pre-trained Transformer-based neural network to generate human-like text in response to user prompts. With its diverse range of training on internet text, ChatGPT can provide responses on various topics, such as general knowledge, conversations, and creative writing.

ğŸ‘‰Q2:What is Google/YouTube Summary with ChatGPT?
ğŸš€A2:It is an extension that displays a summary of ChatGPT in Google search results simultaneously.In addition,you can also get summary of the YouTube videos.

ğŸ‘‰Q3:Is Google/YouTube Summary with ChatGPT free?
ğŸš€Q3:Although our extension is currently free, we are exploring the possibility of introducing a small paywall to sustain the service in the future. By upgrading to the paid service, you will enjoy faster response times, unrestricted access, and high-priority customer support. Our ultimate goal is to provide you with the best possible service in a way that is affordable and accessible to everyone.

ğŸ‘‰Q4:Do I need to create a ChatGPT/OpenAI account to use this extension?
ğŸš€Q4:Yes, you must have a ChatGPT account to use this extension. You can create a free account at chat.openai.com.

â¡ï¸ After install this extension, it will jump to option Page. You can select and set API Provider

â¤ï¸Learn better with ChatGPT 
ğŸ’«How to use it?
â¡ï¸ After install this extension, it will jump to option Page. You can select and set API Provider
â¡ï¸ If you tend to use ChatGPT Webapp as AI Provider, It is free but sometimes unstable,and  mention you "Please login and pass Cloudflare".
â¡ï¸ So we recommend you use your own OpenAI API key. How to get your own OpenAI API key?
â¡ï¸ Login https://platform.openai.com and then click your personal account setting, you can see "View API keys".Finally Create a new secret key or copy the key that you created before.
â¡ï¸ Paste your OpenAI API key to AI Provider and save your config.You can get the summary alongside Google search results or Youtube videos summary now. 

ğŸ™‹Q&A
ğŸ‘‰Q1:What is ChatGPT?
ğŸš€A1:ChatGPT is an OpenAI-developed language model that utilizes a large pre-trained Transformer-based neural network to generate human-like text in response to user prompts. With its diverse range of training on internet text, ChatGPT can provide responses on various topics, such as general knowledge, conversations, and creative writing.

ğŸ‘‰Q2:What is Google/YouTube Summary with ChatGPT?
ğŸš€A2:It is an extension that displays a summary of ChatGPT in Google search results simultaneously.In addition,you can also get summary of the YouTube videos.

ğŸ‘‰Q3:Is Google/YouTube Summary with ChatGPT free?
ğŸš€Q3:Although our extension is currently free, we are exploring the possibility of introducing a small paywall to sustain the service in the future. By upgrading to the paid service, you will enjoy faster response times, unrestricted access, and high-priority customer support. Our ultimate goal is to provide you with the best possible service in a way that is affordable and accessible to everyone.

ğŸ‘‰Q4:Do I need to create a ChatGPT/OpenAI account to use this extension?
ğŸš€Q4:Yes, you must have a ChatGPT account to use this extension. You can create a free account at chat.openai.com.

â¡ï¸ After install this extension, it will jump to option Page. You can select and set API Provider

ğŸš€A1:ChatGPT is an OpenAI-developed language model that utilizes a large pre-trained Transformer-based neural network to generate human-like text in response to user prompts. With its diverse range of training on internet text, ChatGPT can provide responses on various topics, such as general knowledge, conversations, and creative writing.

ğŸ‘‰Q2:What is Google/YouTube Summary with ChatGPT?
ğŸš€A2:It is an extension that displays a summary of ChatGPT in Google search results simultaneously.In addition,you can also get summary of the YouTube videos.

ğŸ‘‰Q3:Is Google/YouTube Summary with ChatGPT free?
ğŸš€Q3:Although our extension is currently free, we are exploring the possibility of introducing a small paywall to sustain the service in the future. By upgrading to the paid service, you will enjoy faster response times, unrestricted access, and high-priority customer support. Our ultimate goal is to provide you with the best possible service in a way that is affordable and accessible to everyone.

â¤ï¸Learn better with ChatGPT 
ğŸ’«How to use it?
â¡ï¸ After install this extension, it will jump to option Page. You can select and set API Provider
â¡ï¸ If you tend to use ChatGPT Webapp as AI Provider, It is free but sometimes unstable,and  mention you "Please login and pass Cloudflare".
â¡ï¸ So we recommend you use your own OpenAI API key. How to get your own OpenAI API key?
â¡ï¸ Login https://platform.openai.com and then click your personal account setting, you can see "View API keys".Finally Create a new secret key or copy the key that you created before.
â¡ï¸ Paste your OpenAI API key to AI Provider and save your config.You can get the summary alongside Google search results or Youtube videos summary now. 

ğŸ™‹Q&A
ğŸ‘‰Q1:What is ChatGPT?
ğŸš€A1:ChatGPT is an OpenAI-developed language model that utilizes a large pre-trained Transformer-based neural network to generate human-like text in response to user prompts. With its diverse range of training on internet text, ChatGPT can provide responses on various topics, such as general knowledge, conversations, and creative writing.

ğŸ‘‰Q2:What is Google/YouTube Summary with ChatGPT?
ğŸš€A2:It is an extension that displays a summary of ChatGPT in Google search results simultaneously.In addition,you can also get summary of the YouTube videos.

ğŸ‘‰Q3:Is Google/YouTube Summary with ChatGPT free?
ğŸš€Q3:Although our extension is currently free, we are exploring the possibility of introducing a small paywall to sustain the service in the future. By upgrading to the paid service, you will enjoy faster response times, unrestricted access, and high-priority customer support. Our ultimate goal is to provide you with the best possible service in a way that is affordable and accessible to everyone.

ğŸ‘‰Q4:Do I need to create a ChatGPT/OpenAI account to use this extension?
ğŸš€Q4:Yes, you must have a ChatGPT account to use this extension. You can create a free account at chat.openai.com.

â¤ï¸Learn better with ChatGPT 
ğŸ’«How to use it?
â¡ï¸ After install this extension, it will jump to option Page. You can select and set API Provider
â¡ï¸ If you tend to use ChatGPT Webapp as AI Provider, It is free but sometimes unstable,and  mention you "Please login and pass Cloudflare".
â¡ï¸ So we recommend you use your own OpenAI API key. How to get your own OpenAI API key?
â¡ï¸ Login https://platform.openai.com and then click your personal account setting, you can see "View API keys".Finally Create a new secret key or copy the key that you created before.
â¡ï¸ Paste your OpenAI API key to AI Provider and save your config.You can get the summary alongside Google search results or Youtube videos summary now. 

ğŸ™‹Q&A
ğŸ‘‰Q1:What is ChatGPT?
ğŸš€A1:ChatGPT is an OpenAI-developed language model that utilizes a large pre-trained Transformer-based neural network to generate human-like text in response to user prompts. With its diverse range of training on internet text, ChatGPT can provide responses on various topics, such as general knowledge, conversations, and creative writing.

ğŸ‘‰Q2:What is Google/YouTube Summary with ChatGPT?
ğŸš€A2:It is an extension that displays a summary of ChatGPT in Google search results simultaneously.In addition,you can also get summary of the YouTube videos.

ğŸ‘‰Q3:Is Google/YouTube Summary with ChatGPT free?
ğŸš€Q3:Although our extension is currently free, we are exploring the possibility of introducing a small paywall to sustain the service in the future. By upgrading to the paid service, you will enjoy faster response times, unrestricted access, and high-priority customer support. ğŸš€Q3:Although our extension is currently free, we are exploring the possibility of introducing a small paywall to sustain the service in the future. By upgrading to the paid service, you will enjoy faster response times, unrestricted access, and high-priority customer support. Our ultimate goal is to provide you with the best possible service in a way that is affordable and accessible to everyone.

ğŸ‘‰Q4:Do I need to create a ChatGPT/OpenAI account to use this extension?
ğŸš€Q4:Yes, you must have a ChatGPT account to use this extension. You can create a free account at chat.openai.com.

â¤ï¸Learn better with ChatGPT 
ğŸ’«How to use it?
â¡ï¸ After install this extension, it will jump to option Page. You can select and set API Provider
â¡ï¸ If you tend to use ChatGPT Webapp as AI Provider, It is free but sometimes unstable,and  mention you "Please login and pass Cloudflare".
â¡ï¸ So we recommend you use your own OpenAI API key. How to get your own OpenAI API key?
â¡ï¸ Login https://platform.openai.com and then click your personal account setting, you can see "View API keys".Finally Create a new secret key or copy the key that you created before.
â¡ï¸ Paste your OpenAI API key to AI Provider and save your config.You can get the summary alongside Google search results or Youtube videos summary now. 

ğŸ™‹Q&A
ğŸ‘‰Q1:What is ChatGPT?
ğŸš€A1:ChatGPT is an OpenAI-developed language model that utilizes a large pre-trained Transformer-based neural network to generate human-like text in response to user prompts. With its diverse range of training on internet text, ChatGPT can provide responses on various topics, such as general knowledge, conversations, and creative writing.

ğŸ‘‰Q2:What is Google/YouTube Summary with ChatGPT?
ğŸš€A2:It is an extension that displays a summary of ChatGPT in Google search results simultaneously.In addition,you can also get summary of the YouTube videos.

ğŸ‘‰Q3:Is Google/YouTube Summary with ChatGPT free?
ğŸš€Q3:Although our extension is currently free, we are exploring the possibility of introducing a small paywall to sustain the service in the future. By upgrading to the paid service, you will enjoy faster response times, unrestricted access, and high-priority customer support. Our ultimate goal is to provide you with the best possible service in a way that is affordable and accessible to everyone.

ğŸ‘‰Q4:Do I need to create a ChatGPT/OpenAI account to use this extension?
ğŸš€Q4:Yes, you must have a ChatGPT account to use this extension. You can create a free account at chat.openai.com.

â¤ï¸Learn better with ChatGPT 
ğŸ’«How to use it?
â¡ï¸ After install this extension, it will jump to option Page. You can select and set API Provider
â¡ï¸ If you tend to use ChatGPT Webapp as AI Provider, It is free but sometimes unstable,and  mention you "Please login and pass Cloudflare".
â¡ï¸ So we recommend you use your own OpenAI API key. How to get your own OpenAI API key?
â¡ï¸ Login https://platform.openai.com and then click your personal account setting, you can see "View API keys".Finally Create a new secret key or copy the key that you created before.
â¡ï¸ Paste your OpenAI API key to AI Provider and save your config.You can get the summary alongside Google search results or Youtube videos summary now. 

ğŸ™‹Q&A
ğŸ‘‰Q1:What is ChatGPT?
ğŸš€A1:ChatGPT is an OpenAI-developed language model that utilizes a large pre-trained Transformer-based neural network to generate human-like text in response to user prompts. With its diverse range of training on internet text, ChatGPT can provide responses on various topics, such as general knowledge, conversations, and creative writing.

ğŸ‘‰Q2:What is Google/YouTube Summary with ChatGPT?
ğŸš€A2:It is an extension that displays a summary of ChatGPT in Google search results simultaneously.In addition,you can also get summary of the YouTube videos.

ğŸ‘‰Q3:Is Google/YouTube Summary with ChatGPT free?
ğŸš€Q3:Although our extension is currently free, we are exploring the possibility of introducing a small paywall to sustain the service in the future. By upgrading to the paid service, you will enjoy faster response times, unrestricted access, and high-priority customer support. Our ultimate goal is to provide you with the best possible service in a way that is affordable and accessible to everyone.

ğŸ‘‰Q4:Do I need to create a ChatGPT/OpenAI account to use this extension?
ğŸš€Q4:Yes, you must have a ChatGPT account to use this extension. You can create a free account at chat.openai.com.
